snippet.title: Graze Counter PV
snippet.description:
Graze the enemy’s bullets, Charge them head-on, and Wreak Havoc!!
An exhilarating and dangerous shoot-em-up! 

Graze Counter is now on steam Greenlight.
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=899022724
Please vote for this game if you are interested in.

This video is edited by Torizenon Productions:
https://www.youtube.com/user/TorizenonProductions
